data.description: This home is about lifestyle! Welcome to Urban OKC Living - Just minutes from the upcoming OakOKC, Mayfair Village, Nichols Hills, Classen Curve, Plaza, and Paseo districts. This large corner lot welcomes you with 2 covered porches (1 front and 1 on the side of the house).  This updated Mayfair Heights home has a two-story floor plan with three living areas downstairs (1 living area and downstairs bath easily converted to downstairs primary suite) and three large bedrooms upstairs. Refinished hardwood floors. Remodeled kitchen with granite counters, farm sink, abundance of cabinet and counter space, pantry, gas cooktop, and stainless appliances.  Updates include new HVAC 2021, garage door opener 2021, and fresh paint 2020.  Downstairs full bath updated with walk in shower.  Backyard is an entertaining oasis with large wood deck (painted 2023) perfect for evening gatherings, firepit, large barn like outbuilding for additional storage, in ground storm shelter and pretty, welcoming flowerbeds.
